{"instruction":"FizzBuzz for numbers 1-15","output":"1 2 Fizz 4 Buzz Fizz 7 8 Fizz Buzz 11 Fizz 13 14 FizzBuzz","whisper":": fizzbuzz {\n  _ 15 > ?? drop ]\n  _ 15 % 0 = ?? \"FizzBuzz\" . drop\n  | _ 3 % 0 = ?? \"Fizz\" . drop\n  | _ 5 % 0 = ?? \"Buzz\" . drop\n  | . ] ] ]\n  1 + fizzbuzz\n} ;\n1 fizzbuzz","python":"for i in range(1,16):\n    if i%15==0: print('FizzBuzz')\n    elif i%3==0: print('Fizz')\n    elif i%5==0: print('Buzz')\n    else: print(i)"}
{"instruction":"Bubble sort a list","input":"[3 1 4 1 5 9 2 6]","output":"[1 1 2 3 4 5 6 9]","whisper":": bubble-step {\n  // implementation\n} ;","python":"def bubble_sort(arr):\n    n = len(arr)\n    for i in range(n):\n        for j in range(0, n-i-1):\n            if arr[j] > arr[j+1]: arr[j], arr[j+1] = arr[j+1], arr[j]\n    return arr"}
{"instruction":"Binary search in sorted list","input":"[1 3 5 7 9 11 13] 7","output":"3","whisper":": binsearch {\n  // implementation\n} ;","python":"def binary_search(arr, target):\n    lo, hi = 0, len(arr)-1\n    while lo <= hi:\n        mid = (lo+hi)//2\n        if arr[mid] == target: return mid\n        elif arr[mid] < target: lo = mid+1\n        else: hi = mid-1\n    return -1"}
